      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. WALKING IN MEMPHIS was heavily backed and justified the support when resuming last start over 1673m at this track (Turf), scoring by 0.3 lengths. Fitter for that last hitout and is the testing material. 4. PARIS SURPRISE settled well back and failed to threaten in the straight last start when tenth, beaten 6 lengths, over this course and distance. Has the talent to find the winners' list. 2. SING SING was in contention on the turn and finished second last time over 1673m at Gulfstream Park All Weather (Synthetic), beaten 2 lengths. Ready to go one better. 3. RUSE ran below expectations last time at this track (Turf), finishing ninth and beaten 5 lengths. Well placed to make amends.\",\"runners\":[1,4,2,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
